snippet.title: Zoe Cannella
snippet.description:
Hi! Thank you for stopping by! I love movies and strive to produce good, entertaining exclusive content! I am so lucky to interview movie stars, attend press screening, red carpets and work on  film reviews.  It is all hand made, tiny budget and for the love of films. I hope you like our original franchise: "Zoe at the Movies". 
I am 13 years old and I am also a VO actor, dancer & singer.

You may also follow me on Instagram: @zoeatthemovies
And check out Facebook: Zoe at the Movies
